{"tid":2098511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度指北京藉不丹邊境爭議向新德里施壓","createTime":"2020-07-07T14:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:05:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4557012b1ab00f25e2324e9b38ad39da6429eead","tid":2098511,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"雖然兩國緊張關係有所緩和，不過爭議並未結束，《印度時報》報道，中國在區內展開了另一條邊境「戰線」。<br />\n<br />\n中方在上月召開的全球環境基金理事會會議中，反對不丹在東部設立薩克滕野生動物保護區，理由是該處屬於中國和不丹之間存在爭議的領土。<br />\n<br />\n報道認為中國對不丹提出新要求，是要藉印度盟向新德里政府施壓，報道又指，不丹駐印度大使館已向中國駐印度大使館發出外交抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部向印度傳媒發出的聲明則指出，中國和不丹的邊界未正式劃定，雙方在東部、中部和西部地區的爭議由來已久，警告第三方不要介入。<br />\n<br />\n復旦大學南亞研究中心副主任林民旺表示，中國和不丹的邊界問題在廿年前基本上已經解決，但基於印度向不丹施壓而無法簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397089&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=3548890f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397089&h=64f7bc6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397089</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cmsimages.tribuneindia.com/gallary_content/2020/7/Desk/2020_7$largeimg_681270233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcmsimages.tribuneindia.com%2Fgallary_content%2F2020%2F7%2FDesk%2F2020_7%24largeimg_681270233.jpg&h=cebfa358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/nation/china-for-border-talks-with-bhutan-india-wary-109532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fchina-for-border-talks-with-bhutan-india-wary-109532&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=f1214092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/nation/china-for-border-talks-with-bhutan-india-wary-109532</a>"}